name: Stay at home [1]
description:
this is a photo of the pillow being dried in the morning.



in Indonesia the first case of the corona virus appeared in April 2020, there is no lockdown term here, there is the term STAY AT HOME, and SOCIAL DISTANCING to reduce the spread of the corona virus.



there is some information that sunbathing can kill the corona virus that is on the surface of objects.



and sunbathing can strengthen our immunity, people are encouraged to sunbathe under the morning sun.
